OL,3,CBristol Airport drop-off charge
OL,4,Cincreases by #1.50
OL,6,FThe fee to drop passengers off at
OL,7,FBristol Airport will rise from #7 to
OL,8,F#8.50 for stays of up to 10 minutes.
OL,10,FAn increased charge comes into effect
OL,11,Ffrom 5 January for the airport's drop
OL,12,Foff and pick up car park and the short
OL,13,Fstay car park, which will rise from #7
OL,14,Fto #8.50 for up to 15 minutes and from
OL,15,F#9 to #10.50 for 15-30 minutes.
OL,17,FIt comes after a series of increases
OL,18,Fover the last few years, rising from
OL,19,F#5 to #6 in 2024 and up to #7 in 2025.
