OL,14,Fit needed to balance protecting
OL,15,Fpeople's jobs while "advancing its
OL,16,Fplans to achieve net zero operations
OL,17,Fby 2030".
OL,19,FThey added that the airport "hopes the
OL,20,Fincreased price would help discourage
OL,21,Fhigh volumes of customers
