OL,6,FAirports are among those facing the
OL,7,Fhighest jump in business rate bills
OL,8,Facross England and Wales because of
OL,9,Fchanges coming into effect next April.
OL,11,FA government spokesperson said:
OL,12,F"Airports are responsible for setting
OL,13,Ftheir own parking terms but must
OL,14,Ffollow consumer law and justify their
OL,15,Fcharges.
OL,17,F"We're delivering a #4.3 billion
OL,18,Fsupport package to cap business rates
OL,19,Fbill increases at 30% before other
OL,20,Freliefs for the largest properties,
OL,21,Fincluding airports.
